  <section class="docstring">



        <div class="specs">

            <pre translate="no"><span class="attribute">-spec</span> tokens_to_string([<a href="../../../../lib/../erts/doc/html/erlang.html#t:term/0">term</a>()]) -> <a href="../../../../lib/../erts/doc/html/erlang.html#t:string/0">string</a>().</pre>

        </div>


<p>Generates a string corresponding to the given token sequence.</p><p>The string can be re-tokenized to yield the same token list again.</p>
